de.mdelab.simulator.events

Class MonitoredPropertyUpdateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mdelab.simulator.events.ChangeEvent
      • de.mdelab.simulator.events.MonitoredPropertyUpdateEvent

  • public class MonitoredPropertyUpdateEvent
extends ChangeEvent
    Change event notifying about an update of the value of a MonitoredProperty. The value can be obtained by MonitoredProperty.getValue().
